{"tid":972327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天主教香港教區宣布，湯漢樞機出任「教區宗座署理」","createTime":"2019-01-07T10:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T04:47:29.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a7859512c44e10604f0e373ceb9a41ae6e559b6c","tid":972327,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:10:59.000Z","msg":"天主教香港教區宣布湯漢樞機出任「教區署理」<br />\n2019-01-07 HKT 17:12<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1436854_1_L_20190107180240.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1436854_1_L_20190107180240.jpg&h=803086b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天主教香港教區宣布，由湯漢樞機出任教區宗座署理。<br />\n<br />\n香港教區秘書長辦公處表示，教區主教公署於上周六下午獲宗座萬民福音部通知，委任漢湯為天主教香港教區宗座署理，負責教區主教出缺期間，治理香港教區，直至另行通知。<br />\n<br />\n湯漢今年79歲，於2009年成為香港教區主教，接替退休的陳日君樞機。湯漢於2014年屆退休的75歲，獲教宗延任3年，直至2017年8月榮休，由楊鳴章接任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1436854-20190107.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1436854-20190107.htm&d=6F2wiYdL7XsyXFQWHa%2BeTWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=f1f4c6a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1436854-20190107.htm&h=5052a12c\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1436854-20190107.htm</a>"},{"pid":"01e22c5984d3845b5024178806399f0631479676","tid":972327,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:12:21.000Z","msg":"tom hank"},{"pid":"4b080c413c96c183527dcd0374149293ec12f22a","tid":972327,"uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T10:13:00.000Z","msg":"頂到80先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a47d7b50a372f62c6f03ef3771d1e5ddb9c7a232","tid":972327,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b080c413c96c183527dcd0374149293ec12f22a","tid":972327,"uid":82640,"li